1
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:36,750
What should we do, Mi Ya?

2
00:01:36,860 --> 00:01:38,660
We’ve looked everywhere around the bar.

3
00:01:38,660 --> 00:01:39,660
No sign of Beidao.

4
00:01:39,780 --> 00:01:41,620
The bar has been closed for days.

5
00:01:41,780 --> 00:01:43,220
I called him a million times

6
00:01:43,220 --> 00:01:44,420
but he didn’t pick up.

7
00:01:45,979 --> 00:01:48,240
Others all say he took the money and left.

8
00:01:48,300 --> 00:01:49,820
He wouldn’t do that.

9
00:01:50,220 --> 00:01:51,820
Where was he staying lately?

10
00:01:51,900 --> 00:01:53,020
At the bar.

11
00:01:53,340 --> 00:01:54,940
Other than going to the grocery,

12
00:01:54,940 --> 00:01:56,259
he seldom left.

13
00:01:56,780 --> 00:01:58,979
Did he say

14
00:01:58,979 --> 00:02:00,310
or do anything strange?

15
00:02:01,940 --> 00:02:03,580
Nothing unusual about his words,

16
00:02:03,580 --> 00:02:05,900
but he did play old songs over and over

17
00:02:06,220 --> 00:02:08,340
as if he was reminiscing about the past.

18
00:02:08,340 --> 00:02:09,259
Mi Ya...

19
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:10,580
I see. Gotta go.

20
00:03:06,220 --> 00:03:07,620
How did you know I’m here?

21
00:03:08,300 --> 00:03:09,180
I took a guess.

22
00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:17,940
I thought you’d be like this forever

23
00:03:18,020 --> 00:03:19,280
and never see me again.

24
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,620
I thought so at first.

25
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:26,300
Mi Ya,

26
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:29,860
thank you.

27
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:33,340
I should thank you.

28
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:37,460
Thank me?

29
00:03:40,140 --> 00:03:41,340
Seeing you here

30
00:03:43,940 --> 00:03:45,260
is a relief.

31
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:08,300
What’s wrong?

32
00:04:10,060 --> 00:04:10,740
Nothing.

33
00:04:12,300 --> 00:04:13,380
Comforting words.

34
00:04:18,779 --> 00:04:19,839
Comforting words?

35
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:24,320
Lu Weixun’s credibility was being questioned.

36
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:26,100
Everything about him

37
00:04:26,100 --> 00:04:27,340
was dug up,

38
00:04:28,380 --> 00:04:30,300
including me writing articles about him

39
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:32,620
on my public account.

40
00:04:33,740 --> 00:04:35,100
My company was affected

41
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:37,030
and lost the compensation.

42
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:38,220
My boss was furious

43
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:41,080
and asked me to delete my account.

44
00:04:42,980 --> 00:04:44,740
After I did it,

45
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:47,220
I felt my years of efforts

46
00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:48,350
went down the drain.

47
00:04:50,820 --> 00:04:52,260
You two are reporters?

48
00:04:52,500 --> 00:04:54,430
Reporters with nothing to report.

49
00:04:54,580 --> 00:04:57,340
I accidentally heard you mentioned Lu Weixun.

50
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:58,140
Yes.

51
00:04:58,220 --> 00:05:00,420
My customers said something about him.

52
00:05:00,420 --> 00:05:01,740
It seems Rose Winery

53
00:05:02,220 --> 00:05:03,660
isn’t his first winery.

54
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:08,500
Sorry,

55
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:11,820
I told the reporters

56
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:14,190
about Lu Weixun’s double identities.

57
00:05:15,940 --> 00:05:16,860
I thought so.

58
00:05:17,580 --> 00:05:18,740
You did?

59
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:21,950
Others all assumed it was Mu Chunfeng.

60
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:25,780
He knew about it long ago.

61
00:05:26,540 --> 00:05:28,860
He wouldn’t wait so long to expose it.

62
00:05:29,780 --> 00:05:30,340
Also,

63
00:05:31,020 --> 00:05:33,220
Mu Chunfeng and I talked about it

64
00:05:35,100 --> 00:05:36,140
at your bar.

65
00:05:36,780 --> 00:05:38,510
How could you be so sure I did it?

66
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:39,780
Because of Buzui.

67
00:05:55,260 --> 00:05:56,340
You don’t blame me?

68
00:05:59,620 --> 00:06:01,180
It’s my fault.

69
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:04,660
I deserve it.

70
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:10,030
You know I disagree with you

71
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:13,260
seeking revenge.

72
00:06:16,380 --> 00:06:17,220
I don’t need

73
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:19,940
anyone’s agreement on that.

74
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:24,340
Why don’t you and He Buzui

75
00:06:24,340 --> 00:06:25,660
talk everything out?

76
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:27,340
How could I?

77
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:30,860
You still won’t quit?

78
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:34,190
I don’t know.

79
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:37,260
All I know is

80
00:06:37,900 --> 00:06:39,420
I’m the only one left.

81
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:46,560
After all these years,

82
00:06:48,260 --> 00:06:49,220
I still can’t

83
00:06:50,420 --> 00:06:52,500
forget about those things.

84
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:55,700
Mi Ya,

85
00:06:57,940 --> 00:07:00,020
I can’t, I can’t let it go.

86
00:07:00,060 --> 00:07:01,940
I just want a result.

87
00:07:05,260 --> 00:07:06,180
Is that wrong?

88
00:07:11,180 --> 00:07:11,900
Fine.

89
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:15,540
It’s not wrong.

90
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:19,220
Don’t wrong a good man

91
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:21,700
and never let a bad man go.

92
00:07:28,180 --> 00:07:28,980
But

93
00:07:32,740 --> 00:07:34,600
you need to take care of yourself.

94
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:36,140
Hey, Nanke,

95
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:38,260
don’t be afraid.

96
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:42,180
Continue.

97
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:49,300
People and things come and go

98
00:07:49,740 --> 00:07:53,860
Experienced love and hurt

99
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:58,460
Pain might be gone

100
00:07:58,659 --> 00:08:00,740
But

101
00:08:00,860 --> 00:08:03,580
The scar is still there

102
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:07,700
Keep chasing after the desire

103
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:11,740
It vanished

104
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:16,300
Can you be yourself again

105
