260
00:17:26,180 --> 00:17:27,900
Sweet and sour ribs.

261
00:17:29,820 --> 00:17:30,340
Fine.

262
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:32,140
We’ll have ribs.

263
00:17:32,700 --> 00:17:33,180
Take it.

264
00:17:34,180 --> 00:17:35,380
I’ll go buy some ribs.

265
00:17:35,420 --> 00:17:36,340
Be back soon.

266
00:17:36,780 --> 00:17:37,140
OK.

267
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:38,040
Have some rest.

268
