271
00:18:46,180 --> 00:18:47,980
You should go back to the WSA.

272
00:18:50,060 --> 00:18:51,540
I don’t want to.

273
00:18:52,300 --> 00:18:54,940
The total lunar eclipse is tonight.

274
00:18:55,140 --> 00:18:56,300
Watch it with me.

275
00:18:56,620 --> 00:18:58,300
I can ask Patrick for a few days off.

276
00:18:58,300 --> 00:18:59,100
Problem solved.

277
00:18:59,100 --> 00:19:00,620
I’m too busy

278
00:19:00,780 --> 00:19:01,820
to be with you.

279
00:19:03,020 --> 00:19:04,150
What about He Buzui?

280
00:19:04,900 --> 00:19:05,760
What about her?

281
00:19:05,900 --> 00:19:07,300
Isn’t she your assistant?

282
00:19:07,300 --> 00:19:08,620
Give your work to her.

283
00:19:08,900 --> 00:19:11,220
I need to handle these things on my own.

284
00:19:13,260 --> 00:19:15,300
I’m your fiancée.

285
00:19:15,380 --> 00:19:16,980
I want your company.

286
00:19:17,100 --> 00:19:18,340
- Also...  - Bai Jing,

287
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:20,980
stop!

288
00:19:28,740 --> 00:19:29,870
Where are you going?

289
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:30,640
Emergency.

290
00:19:30,980 --> 00:19:32,140
Mr. Ma will give you a ride.

291
00:19:32,140 --> 00:19:33,340
Once you’re back in France,

292
00:19:33,340 --> 00:19:35,070
bring my greetings to Patrick.

293
00:19:37,100 --> 00:19:38,740
I don’t need a ride.

294
00:19:46,100 --> 00:19:46,780
You like it?

295
00:19:48,580 --> 00:19:49,300
Yeah!

